  "name": "Rhodos Horizon City",
  "description": "Our magnificent fully refurbished adults-only hotel (minimum age 16+) “Rhodos Horizon City” (ex- “Constantin”) is now under new management and ownership. Its privileged location in the heart of Rhodes Town, opposite the Casino, 250 meters to the beach, 750 meters to the historical Old Town (Medieval City), with Grand’s Master Palace and The Street of Knights. Diagoras International Airport is only 15 km from the hotel, 1,7 km to the Main Port of Rhodes. Our hotel is comprised of 149 spacious, modern, and elegant rooms and suites with incredible views of the city of Rhodes. The Island Suites are all located on the executive top floor with breathtaking views and VIP amenities. Apart from our famous Island suites, you can also choose the City Suite or the Junior Suite. Our classic twin rooms are with either Sea view, Limited Sea view, or Inland view. Rhodos Horizon City operates on Bed and Breakfast basis but there is also an “A la Carte” restaurant on-site for our designated guests and a Bar. Guests can relax and enjoy a drink at our outdoor pool with fresh water. Sunbeds and umbrellas are provided at no extra charge as well as the pool towels. The hotel supplies a well-equipped fitness center (free of charge), a sauna (free of charge), a game room with billiards (extra charge), and table tennis(free of charge).",
